data.description: Located on secluded Snead Island, this home is the perfect retreat away from all of the hustle and bustle that comes to our state every year. As your drive through the island, you'll enjoy all of the natural Florida foliage and picture-perfect views. If you are a nature lover, this home is just a mile away from Emerson Preserve. If you prefer boating, there is a marina and the Bradenton Yacht Club is just a few blocks away. When you are done exploring, you can sit by your pool or relax in your spa. With 4 bedrooms, there is plenty of room for your family or guests. A wonderful home for entertaining.  You'll notice the open floor plan that will allow your to make this home your own. The home has two AC's, 1 of two of the AC's was replaced in 2018, and a new metal roof in 2012. For the investor, close up the stairs and convert the garage  Stop by and see for yourself all that this wonderful Florida home has to offer.
